text:
{
  "prompt": "A high-performance electric kickboard modified with a comfortable motorcycle-style saddle installed. The design features a dual-motor setup, wide 11-inch tires, a robust aluminum frame with front and rear suspension. The battery is mounted under the deck, and the rear includes a small cargo rack with integrated LED lighting. The handlebar resembles a motorcycle's, with a digital dashboard. The overall color scheme is sleek black and red, with aerodynamic lines and a premium industrial finish. The scene is well-lit, side view angle, studio background.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A high-performance electric scooter designed for urban commuting, equipped with a large 72V 120Ah battery integrated into the low deck. The scooter features a matte black aerodynamic body, dual rear shock absorbers, thick 11-inch tubeless tires, and a comfortable wide motorcycle-style seat. The handlebars have a digital display and mirrors, and the rear includes a cargo rack. It is parked on a road surrounded by trees and open green space in the background, under bright daylight.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A high-performance electric scooter parked on a paved path in a park under bright daylight. The scooter features a matte black frame with an extended wheelbase, clearly 200mm longer than standard. It includes a cushioned seat, large tires, and a visible 72V 120AH battery compartment integrated in the center. The design emphasizes stability and long-range performance. The lush green park and blue sky provide a vibrant backdrop.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
